<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrīśakāb<unclear>dā</unclear>lu 1044 
<lb n="2"/>nēṇṭi kanyāmāsa śuklapakṣa 
<lb n="3"/>Ēkādasiyu sōmavāramu 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>na niḍuṁjeṟvuna nīlīsvara 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>dēvaraku guṇḍamaseṭṭi<unclear>yu</unclear> 
<lb n="6"/>Eṟapōtaseṭṭiyuṁ dama 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>taṇḍri kaṁṭamaseṭṭi pēruse 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ppi peṭṭu Akhaṇḍavarttidivi 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ya 1ṇṭi māḍa 5 Ācaṁdrā 
<lb n="10" break="no"/>rkamu naḍapaṁggalavāru prōlā 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>carivrālu 
</p>

